data.message:
Very disappointed this year!! No stalls by the wheel. (No pork scratching and no cider!!!)
 Alot smaller than last year and not the same buzz as it had in previous years.

Bit disappointed this year, me and partner been coming last 3yrs, the last 2yrs we always gone to 1 craft stall and bring home a little Christmas ornament, but the lovely lady wasn't there :( and considering the market is there till 29th it was a shame to see yesterday alot of the craft stalls by library packed up and gone :(
